article_metadata.author: Stephen Moore

og.description: Among so many of President Obama's flaws, near the top of the list is that he has never understood the art of the deal. Every successful president has cut deals with the other party to strategically advance his own agenda. Give a little, get a little. Washington, Lincoln, FDR, Reagan [...]
